GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
110: 22
***
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of
the Council of Ministers that Shrimati Violet Alva, assumed
office as Deputy Minister with effect from after-noon of
the 23rd April, 1957. She will be attached to the Ministry
of Home Affairs, and designated as Deputy Minister of Home
Affairs.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy tos-
Ashill
(A.S. Gill)
for Secretary. to the Cabinet.
